### FoxxMC application for <description>

## For install as global package
```
sudo npm i -g git+https://<username>:<password>@bitbucket.org/foxxmc/foxxmc.git#1.0.0
```

## For creation new empty app
```
mkdir <app_name>
cd <app_name>
foxx init <app_name>
```

## For creation new boilerplate app
```
mkdir <app_name>
cd <app_name>
foxx init <app_name> --boilerplate
```

## For start in development
```
cd <app_name>
foxx watch
```

## For build production distrib
```
cd <app_name>
foxx build
```

## Generators usage (in <app_name> folder)
```
foxx generate model tomato
foxx g controller cucumber
foxx g mixin entry
```

## Available generators:
* controller
* mixin
* migration
* model
* script


## Usefull command in console for creation ssh agent
```
eval `ssh-agent -s`
ssh-add ~/.ssh/id_rsa

```

